.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, action, musical, family
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the german is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching western movies##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | western   | family | action |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

