.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
City: berlin, miami, venice, paris
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person traveling to venice is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
6. the person traveling to paris is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to miami##7
7. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| City   | berlin    | paris | miami   | venice |

