.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, april, may
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| Birthday   | november | april | may    | september |

