There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, biathlon, water-polo, volleyball
1. the argentine is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
3. the spanish is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Sport           | water-polo   | volleyball    | snowboarding       | biathlon  |

