4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person who's birthday is in march##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
