4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person eating asparagus##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating zucchini and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person eating lime##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | hiking | collecting | filmmaking | fishing |
| Food   | zucchini   | cabbage      | asparagus        | lime  |

