4. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
