.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, june, march
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, train
1. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in september##7
2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the train##2
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
6. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Birthday    | september   | may  | march  | june |
| Transport   | jet-ski | quad-bike | bike | train    |

